AUDIO: 'I can help you with? That\'s it. Thank you. Okay, so let\'s talk about what just happened. The avatars here are from Keyframe Labs, hyperrealistic and emotionally expressive. It doesn\'t just lip sync, it reads the emotional context'

[01:42] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'from the conversation and shifts its its expression in real time from sad to happy to offended. And that all happened automatically through the Life Kit agents Eframe plugin. Now, the handoff'

[01:54] [scene:talk]
